name: Non Fungible Cards collection 04 - Manage your Crypto Assets
description: An asset is anything of value or a resource that can be converted into cash. The cattle of this farmer in the Amazon rainforest is an important asset for him. This token may be an important asset for you, and me. But for sure the rainforest is an important asset for everybody. We are still in 2021, and this token is meant to remind us that, at this moment of time, it was easier to find value for a digital token than for the Amazon rainforest.
